title: 11/16: Mailbag! (Record Fri.) (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Going through the big news including Jay Ajayi's potential return to PHI (2:30). Should you add him? If Jordan Howard is out, will Miles Sanders be a stud against NE? Then we talk DFS (7:45) with some tips for this week, read your Apple Podcast questions (11:48), do a little Regulatin' (18:00) and then get to your trade questions (22:00) and Start or Sit questions (30:50) at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
